    "description": "Baroque Japan Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the retail and wholesale of apparel and accessories in Japan, China, Hong Kong, South Korea, and the United States. It designs and sells clothing apparel for women, men, and kids, as well as fashion and home accessories under various brands, including MOUSSY, SLY, SHEL'TTER, rienda, AZUL BY MOUSY, RODEO CROWNS WIDE BOWL, ENFÖLD, STACCATO, RIM.ARK, någonstans, R4G, STYLEMIXER, LAGUA GEM, HeRIN.CYE, SHEL'TTER GREEN, TUIN greenery, MOUSSY VINTAGE, and OUTLET. The company is also involved in quality, brand, and trademark management businesses. It sells its products through retail and web stores. The company was formerly known as Baroque Holdings Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Baroque Japan Limited in February 2008. Baroque Japan Limited was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Meguro, Japan."
